  "texts": [
    "The organization of this paper is as follows: We first review the theoretical and empirical context surrounding ATS, feedback, GLM architectures, and GLM training.",
    "We then detail the characteristics of the data, models, prompts, and training methods used in this study.",
    "Our results are divided into (A) AES and ASAS performance and (B) evaluation of feedback (of essays and short answers, respectively).",
    "Finally, we discuss some of the ramifications of our findings and suggest avenues for future research.",
    "In addition to this paper, for greater transparency, we make publicly available the scores and feedback generated by our fine-tuned GLMs."
  ],
